00:11:11.790 --> 00:11:17.400
Sometimes art is supposed to be difficult to get.

00:11:17.400 --> 00:11:19.897
For example, I have another novel here::

00:11:19.897 --> 00:11:23.460
"What It Feels Like For
a Girl" by Paris Lees.

00:11:23.460 --> 00:11:26.100
Full disclosure, Paris is
one of my best friends,

00:11:26.100 --> 00:11:27.930
but I liked her novel before we met.

00:11:27.930 --> 00:11:29.700
It's about a kid called Byron

00:11:29.700 --> 00:11:31.320
who grows up on a council estate

00:11:31.320 --> 00:11:33.870
in the Midlands and has
a really rough time.

00:11:33.870 --> 00:11:35.641
And the whole thing is written

00:11:35.641 --> 00:11:38.610
in the dialect of that region.

00:11:38.610 --> 00:11:39.930
If you're not from

00:11:39.930 --> 00:11:43.692
that specific geographic
and socioeconomic place,

00:11:43.692 --> 00:11:46.080
it is sometimes hard to interpret.

00:11:46.080 --> 00:11:51.080
And that's a good thing because,
spoilers, Byron is trans,

00:11:51.810 --> 00:11:53.460
which is also never explained.

00:11:53.460 --> 00:11:55.560
There's never a scene where
like a doctor turns up

00:11:55.560 --> 00:11:57.990
and explains to the audience
what trans people are

00:11:57.990 --> 00:12:00.330
and confirms that Byron is one.

00:12:00.330 --> 00:12:02.668
The reader's struggle
to interpret the text

00:12:02.668 --> 00:12:05.880
parallels Byron's own
struggle to just live,

00:12:05.880 --> 00:12:09.120
free of the interpretations
other people push on them.

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:12.660
The challenge to the reader
is, even if you don't 100%

00:12:12.660 --> 00:12:17.430
understand this person, can
you still feel for them?

00:12:17.430 --> 00:12:21.150
So in a way, if you 100% got it,

00:12:21.150 --> 00:12:22.597
you'd almost be missing out!

00:12:22.597 --> 00:12:26.850
"Interpretation is the revenge
of the intellect upon art.

00:12:26.850 --> 00:12:28.530
Even more, it is the revenge

00:12:28.530 --> 00:12:30.540
of the intellect upon the world.

00:12:30.540 --> 00:12:32.760
To interpret is to impoverish,

00:12:32.760 --> 00:12:35.370
to deplete the world in order to set up

00:12:35.370 --> 00:12:37.590
a shadow world of meanings.

00:12:37.590 --> 00:12:41.400
Real art has the capacity
to make us nervous.

00:12:41.400 --> 00:12:44.457
Interpretation makes art
manageable, conformable."

